      },
      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Gales of Ibushi Blow Again",
        "Client": "Guild Master Hojo",
        "Description": "Worrying news indeed... Ibushi\r\nhas been spotted in the Coral\r\nPalace. Fortunately, it has yet\r\nto meet up with its queen, but\r\nI have a terrible feeling... Hunter,\r\nyou must leap into action at once.\r\nWe cannot allow them to reunite!",
        "Target": "Slay Wind Serpent Ibushi",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "L\u0027Ibushi souffle de nouveau",
        "Client": "Hojo le M. de la Guilde",
        "Description": "Inqui\u00E9tant en effet... L\u0027Ibushi\r\na \u00E9t\u00E9 aper\u00E7u au Palais de coraux.\r\nHeureusement, il n\u0027a pas encore\r\nretrouv\u00E9 sa reine, mais j\u0027ai un\r\nmauvais pressentiment...\r\nTu dois intervenir au plus vite\r\npour les emp\u00EAcher de se r\u00E9unir !",
        "Target": "Tuer l\u0027Ibushi du vent",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0/Temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "L\u0027Ibushi colpisce ancora",
        "Client": "Hojo il capo della Gilda",
        "Description": "Notizie allarmanti... L\u0027Ibushi\r\n\u00E8 stato avvistato al Palazzo\r\ncorallino. Per fortuna non ha\r\nancora incontrato la sua\r\nregina, ma ho una brutta\r\nsensazione... Entra subito in\r\nazione! Non devono riunirsi!",
        "Target": "Uccidi l\u0027Ibushi del vento",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "St\u00FCrme Ibushis w\u00FCten wieder",
        "Client": "Gildenmeister Hojo",
        "Description": "\u00DCble Nachrichten... Ibushi\r\nwurde im Korallenpalast ge-\r\nsichtet. Er hat seine K\u00F6nigin\r\nnoch nicht gefunden, aber ich\r\nhab ein schlechtes Gef\u00FChl...\r\nDu musst handeln. Sie d\u00FCrfen\r\nnicht zusammenkommen!",
        "Target": "Erlege Windschlange Ibushi.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Vuelve el vendaval de Ibushi",
        "Client": "Hojo el maestro del gremio",
        "Description": "Tengo nuevas preocupantes...\r\nHan visto a Ibushi en el Palacio\r\ncoralino. Por suerte, a\u00FAn no ha\r\nllegado su reina, pero tengo un\r\nmal presentimiento... \u003CLSNR {cazador} {cazadora}\u003E,\r\nhas de actuar en seguida. \u00A1No\r\npodemos permitir que se re\u00FAnan!",
        "Target": "Abate a Ibushi de viento",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u0412\u043E\u0440\u043E\u0442\u0430 \u0418\u0431\u0443\u0441\u0438 \u0441\u043D\u043E\u0432\u0430 \u0432\u0437\u043E\u0440\u0432\u0430\u043D\u044B",
        "Client": "\u041C\u0430\u0441\u0442\u0435\u0440 \u0413\u0438\u043B\u044C\u0434\u0438\u0438 \u0425\u043E\u0434\u0437\u0451",
        "Description": "\u0422\u0440\u0435\u0432\u043E\u0436\u043D\u044B\u0435 \u043D\u043E\u0432\u043E\u0441\u0442\u0438... \u0418\u0431\u0443\u0441\u0438\r\n\u043E\u0431\u043D\u0430\u0440\u0443\u0436\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0432\u043E \u0414\u0432\u043E\u0440\u0446\u0435 \u043A\u043E\u0440\u0430\u043B\u043B\u043E\u0432.\r\n\u041A \u0441\u0447\u0430\u0441\u0442\u044C\u044E, \u043E\u043D \u0435\u0449\u0435 \u043D\u0435\r\n\u0432\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0435\u0442\u0438\u043B\u0441\u044F \u0441\u043E \u0441\u0432\u043E\u0435\u0439 \u043A\u043E\u0440\u043E\u043B\u0435\u0432\u043E\u0439,\r\n\u043D\u043E \u0443 \u043C\u0435\u043D\u044F \u0443\u0436\u0430\u0441\u043D\u043E\u0435\r\n\u043F\u0440\u0435\u0434\u0447\u0443\u0432\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0438\u0435. \u0421\u043A\u043E\u0440\u0435\u0435 \u043F\u043E\u043C\u043E\u0433\u0438!\r\n\u041D\u0435\u043B\u044C\u0437\u044F \u0434\u0430\u0442\u044C \u0438\u043C \u0432\u0441\u0442\u0440\u0435\u0442\u0438\u0442\u044C\u0441\u044F!",
        "Target": "\u0423\u0431\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0417\u043C\u0435\u044F \u0432\u0435\u0442\u0440\u0430 \u0418\u0431\u0443\u0441\u0438",
        "Fail": "\u0421\u0447\u0435\u0442\u0447\u0438\u043A \u043D\u0430\u0433\u0440\u0430\u0434\u044B \u0434\u043E\u0445\u043E\u0434\u0438\u0442 \u0434\u043E 0\r\n\u0438\u043B\u0438 \u0438\u0441\u0442\u0435\u043A\u0430\u0435\u0442 \u0432\u0440\u0435\u043C\u044F"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Wichry Ibushiego zn\u00F3w wiej\u0105",
        "Client": "Mistrz Gildii Hojo",
        "Description": "Niepokoj\u0105ce wie\u015Bci... W Koralowym\r\nPa\u0142acu widziano Ibushiego. Na\r\nszcz\u0119\u015Bcie jeszcze nie znalaz\u0142\r\nswojej kr\u00F3lowej, ale mam straszne\r\nprzeczucia... Musisz natychmiast\r\nwkroczy\u0107 do akcji. Ta dw\u00F3jka nie\r\nmo\u017Ce si\u0119 ponownie spotka\u0107!",
